      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">19.1508</ph> 
         <?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2016-011?>Contract clauses.<?FM MARKER [Why] Revise section 19.1508.?></title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d1255e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1291e12" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>The contracting officer shall insert
the clause at <xref href="52.219-29.dita#FAR_52_219_29"
                        base="i1057902"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.219-29</xref>,
Notice of Set-Aside for, or Sole-Source Award to, Economically Disadvantaged
Women-owned Small Business Concerns, in solicitations and contracts
for acquisitions that are set aside or awarded on a sole-source
basis to, EDWOSB concerns under <xref href="19.1505.dita#FAR_19_1505"
                        base="i1099249"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.1505</xref>(b)
or <xref href="19.1506.dita#FAR_19_1506"
                        base="i1099284"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.1506</xref>(a). This includes
multiple-award contracts when orders may be set aside for EDWOSB
concerns as described in <xref href="8.405-5.dita#FAR_8_405_5"
                        base="i1117805"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">8.405-5</xref> and <xref href="16.505.dita#FAR_16_505"
                        base="i1104008"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">16.505</xref>(b)(2)(i)(F) or when
orders may be issued directly to one EDWOSB contractor in accordance
with <xref href="19.504.dita#FAR_19_504"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.504</xref>(c)(1)(ii).</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1291e36" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>The contracting
officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="52.219-30.dita#FAR_52_219_30"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.219-30</xref>,
Notice of Set-Aside for, or Sole-Source Award to, Women-Owned Small
Business Concerns Eligible Under the Women-Owned Small Business
Program, in solicitations and contracts for acquisitions that are
set aside or awarded on a sole-source basis to WOSB concerns under <xref href="19.1505.dita#FAR_19_1505"
                        base="i1099249"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.1505</xref>(c) or <xref href="19.1506.dita#FAR_19_1506"
                        base="i1099284"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.1506</xref>(b). This includes
multiple-award contracts when orders may be set aside for WOSB concerns
eligible under the WOSB Program as described in <xref href="8.405-5.dita#FAR_8_405_5"
                        base="i1117805"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">8.405-5</xref> and <xref href="16.505.dita#FAR_16_505"
                        base="i1104008"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">16.505</xref>(b)(2)(i)(F) or
when orders may be issued directly to one WOSB contractor in accordance
with <xref href="19.504.dita#FAR_19_504"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.504</xref>(c)(1)(ii).</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1291e60" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>For use of clause <xref href="52.219-14.dita#FAR_52_219_14"
                        base="i1057823"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.219-14</xref>, Limitations
on Subcontracting, see the prescription at <xref href="19.507.dita#FAR_19_507"
                        base="id203CEK0I0HS"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.507</xref>(e).</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1291e71" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>For use of clause <xref href="52.219-33.dita#FAR_52_219_33"
                        base="i1057823"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.219-33</xref>, Nonmanufacturer
Rule, see the prescription at <xref href="19.507.dita#FAR_19_507"
                        base="id203CEK0I0HS"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">19.507</xref>(h).</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
